Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.25,0:00:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇!旅途中能到這種海灘來\N真是太幸運了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.86,0:00:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天果然就是該到海水浴場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.10,0:00:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也該輕鬆一下呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.20,0:00:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史派克，不下來游泳嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.27,0:00:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服喔，哈哈哈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.12,0:00:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 救命呀\N- 鯊…鯊魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.55,0:00:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我啊妮絲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.73,0:00:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這見習騎士馬上就去救妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.83,0:00:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?這不是劍啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.26,0:00:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點救我!史派克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.27,0:01:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要過來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.42,0:01:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，得救了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.11,0:01:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪、怪物!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.42,0:01:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.98,0:01:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是鯊魚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.17,0:01:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是那個魚鰭的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.36,0:01:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是龍寶寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.99,0:01:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 等等啊…\N- 咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.30,0:01:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了…史派克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.24,0:01:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怪叔叔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.01,0:01:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想來送魔法劍的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.11,0:01:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了找史派克還漂流這麼久…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.89,0:01:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經是叔叔輩的嗎?
